{"tid":1282260,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"如果想賠＄比立法會餐廳老闆請入","createTime":"2019-07-03T13:58:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-03T14:05:41.000Z","uid":260093,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ed5290366fe32ca25d9b78a9edfb5816bd343c26","tid":1282260,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:58:18.000Z","msg":"立法會餐廳李老闆係<span style=\"color: red;\">嘉嘉得飲食有限公司董事李先生</span><br />\n<br />\n佢<span style=\"color: green;\">好似</span>係<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港仔黃竹坑道18號瑞琪工業大廈地下</span></span>有餐廳叫GaGa Restaurant。<br />\n<br />\n唔該巴打幫手fact check下<span style=\"font-size: small;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span><br />\n<br />\n如果係真嘅話，大家可以將汽水/道歉信件 寄過去嗰度。<br />\n<br />\n寄嘅時候，記得要寫明原因<br />\n～例如：賠償我地入去嘅時候拎走嘅嘢飲<br />\n<br />\n唔好俾老闆收得咁莫名其妙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: purple;\">唔該巴打幫我Fact Check 下先</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"720bd753ae7e7bddca9bb46eeb4ee366b72daf98","tid":1282260,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:59:10.000Z","msg":"搵個可靠嘅人幫手Fact Check 下<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdc39a28953aa8c5d57fad2bcae92fe338e55956","tid":1282260,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:59:20.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"414a4ad3703c049a34e44a97f0dc508e38216ee4","tid":1282260,"uid":260093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-03T13:59:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"4ae57fe1cda2891233a025ddc5819c